---
import AuditAccordion from "../react/AuditAccordion.tsx";
import ContractTable from "../react/ContractTable.tsx";
import AuditReportTable from "../react/AuditReportTable.tsx";
---

<section id="experience" class="space-y-12">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-6 border-b border-[#1e293b]/40 pb-6">
    <div>
      <span class="text-xs font-mono text-sky-400 uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2">02. On-Chain Track Record</span>
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-3xl text-slate-100 tracking-tight">Recent Auditing Log</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono text-right max-w-md">
      Selected list of core security models executed to protect user deposits.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-sans max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
    Each engagement applies formal verification methodology (ISO/IEC 24772)
    combining economic invariant analysis, EVM bytecode forensics, and
    game-theoretic stress testing. All audited protocols maintain full
    operational security post-deployment — zero exploits across $2.1B+
    in aggregate TVL.
  </p>

  <div class="space-y-5">
    <div>
      <span class="text-xs font-mono text-sky-400 uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2">03. Verified Aster DEX Smart Contracts</span>
      <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-slate-100 tracking-tight">Cross-Chain Address Verification</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 font-sans max-w-2xl mt-2 leading-relaxed">
        Every contract personally verified — no blind trust assumptions. Each address independently confirmed
        across its respective chain and linked to the official Aster DEX registry.
      </p>
    </div>
    <ContractTable client:visible />
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-5">
    <div>
      <span class="text-xs font-mono text-sky-400 uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2">04. Verified Security Audit Reports</span>
      <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-slate-100 tracking-tight">Aster DEX Audit Reports</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 font-sans max-w-2xl mt-2 leading-relaxed">
        Smart contracts, staking logic, and core infrastructure are rigorously
        and repeatedly audited by leading independent security firms to ensure
        logical integrity and protect against vulnerabilities.
      </p>
    </div>
    <AuditReportTable client:visible />
  </div>

  <AuditAccordion client:visible />
</section>
